  <h1>ColorClip Pro Documentation</h1>

  <p>
    Welcome to the ColorClip Pro documentation! This guide will help you get the most
    out of your color management workflow.
  </p>

  <div class="quick-start-box">
    <h3>Quick Start Guide</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Install ColorClip Pro</li>
      <li>Create your first palette</li>
